{"word":"δικαιολογέομαι","slug":"δικαιολογέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δικαιολογέομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:λόγος'><el>λόγος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to plead one's cause before the judge</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a>, <el>οἱ δικαιολογοῦντες</el> <i>advocates</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}